==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blood-boltered
<hw>Blood"-bol`tered</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Blood</ets> + Prov. E. <ets>bolter</ets> to mat in tufts. Cf.
<er>Balter</er>.]</ety> <def>Having the hair matted with clotted
blood.</def> <mark>[Obs. & R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>blood-boltered</qex> Banquo smiles upon me.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>bloodcurdling</ent>⟦br⟧
